snippet.textDisplay: Everything in its original shape and colour has a different taste and beauty than mixed with artificial sounds. I don't like Coke Studio diluting the pure Balochi 'Nad Sur'. People who are specialist in 'Nad Sur' or accustomed to listing it will tell that the 'Sur' throat singing is not in its original shape in this music. Sur sound better when the 'Surri' throat singer is allowed to sing freely and not controled by either other people or electronic devices.
snippet.textOriginal: Everything in its original shape and colour has a different taste and beauty than mixed with artificial sounds. I don't like Coke Studio diluting the pure Balochi 'Nad Sur'. People who are specialist in 'Nad Sur' or accustomed to listing it will tell that the 'Sur' throat singing is not in its original shape in this music. Sur sound better when the 'Surri' throat singer is allowed to sing freely and not controled by either other people or electronic devices.
